                     <interp inst="t18160529-121-off648" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160529-121-off648" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160529-121-cd649" type="crimeDate">16th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160529-121-off648 t18160529-121-cd649"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 5s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160529-121-victim1072" type="victimName">
                           George 
