                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160529-121-defend1070 t18160529-121-punish652"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
